data.description: This fabulous townhouse in Lorraine Lakes has many great features. It is an end-unit, providing additional privacy and natural light. The community offers a resort-like atmosphere with amenities such as a pool, clubhouse, restaurant, game room, kid's park, workout rooms, and an indoor basketball court. The home has an open and inviting floor plan, featuring all gas appliances. There is an attached garage for convenience. The property also has a lanai that overlooks a scenic lake. The location is ideal, being near the new library, Premier Sports, and easy access to Route 70. It is also within close proximity to all the amenities and attractions of the Lakewood Ranch community. If you are interested in this townhouse, it is currently vacant and available for immediate move-in. The community is gated, so be sure to call ahead before visiting.
